&mt LSHFT SPACE  &kp SEMICOLON     &kp COLON          &kp QUESTION  &kp LEFT_BRACE        &kp RIGHT_BRACE            &trans     &kp NUMBER_1  &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &trans     &trans
&trans           &kp ENTER         &kp ENTER                        &kp ENTER             &kp ENTER                  &kp ENTER  &kp N0                      &kp PERIOD    &trans     &trans
&kp LEFT         &kp UP            &kp SPACE          &kp DOWN      &kp RIGHT                                                   &kp HOME      &kp PG_UP     &kp ENTER     &kp PG_DN  &kp END
                                                      &kp A                                                                                   &kp B
